--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.2 (2019-02-05)
E: Use Jinja2 argument 'indentfirst' instead of 'first' (support older Jinja2 versions)

* Version 0.4.1 (2019-02-03)
E: Improve Jinja2 indent filter

* Version 0.4.0 (2019-01-31)
C: Redesign 'prometheus_scrape_configs' option (alter config variable to string)
F: Update 'prometheus' to version '2.7.1'

* Version 0.3.0 (2019-01-28)
C: Rename option 'prometheus_storage_tsdb_retention' to 'prometheus_storage_tsdb_retention_time'
F: Update 'prometheus' to version '2.7.0'

* Version 0.2.0 (2019-01-21)
C: Manage configuration file 'prometheus.yml'
F: Add support for 'evaluation_interval' option (prometheus_global_evaluation_interval)
F: Add support for 'scrape_interval' option (prometheus_global_scrape_interval)
F: Add support for 'scrape_configs' option (prometheus_scrape_configs)

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-01-16)
F: Initial release
